<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Welcome to Ostora</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); padding: 40px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;">
    <h1 style="color: white; margin: 0; font-size: 36px;">Welcome to Ostora!</h1>
    <p style="color: white; margin: 10px 0 0 0;">Your journey to the perfect job starts here</p>
  </div>
  
  <div style="background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;">
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    
    <p>Welcome to Ostora! We're excited to have you on board. 🎉</p>
    
    <p>Ostora is your AI-powered job search platform that helps you find and apply to jobs faster and smarter.</p>
    
    <h3 style="color: #667eea;">Here's what you can do:</h3>
    
    <div style="background: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0;">
      <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>🔍 Smart Job Search</strong> - Find jobs that match your skills and preferences</p>
    </div>
    
    <div style="background: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0;">
      <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>📄 AI-Powered CV Analysis</strong> - Get insights on how to improve your resume</p>
    </div>
    
    <div style="background: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0;">
      <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>✉️ Auto-Apply</strong> - Apply to multiple jobs with one click</p>
    </div>
    
    <div style="background: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0;">
      <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>📊 Application Tracking</strong> - Monitor all your applications in one place</p>
    </div>
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" style="background: #667eea; color: white; padding: 15px 40px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold;">Get Started</a>
    </div>
    
    <p>Need help? Check out our <a href="{{helpUrl}}" style="color: #667eea;">Help Center</a> or reply to this email.</p>
    
    <p>Happy job hunting!</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>The Ostora Team</p>
    
    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; margin: 30px 0;">
    
    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999; text-align: center;">
      © 2024 Ostora. All rights reserved.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
